title: Luciano Pavarotti  Favorite Neapolitan Songs 320k musicfromrizzo
description:
My two most favorite songs by Pavarotti of the greatest songs of Italy
are "Non ti scordar di me" and "Caruso" they are to be found on CDs 
we've previously uploaded here too such as the "song book CD".

As for this Favorite Neapolitan Songs CD, there's some great Pavarotti
standard selections to be found and standards of the genre. Enjoy this
greatest of all voices ever in this world of our own.

Please seed if you like the music - with thanks, grazie

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
